node.text:
Step into Steph's booth as the all-new radio show host for KRCT: Haven's best - and only - radio station. Over four seasons, discover more about Steph's past and her relationships as she makes her mark on the record store, uncovers its secrets – and decides her future.

Life is Strange: True Colors is out September 10, with Steph's DLC, 'Wavelengths', available September 30 on PlayStation, Xbox, PC, and Stadia, and coming to Nintendo Switch later this year.

Pre-order now through the link in our bio!

node.title: Life is Strange: True Colors - Steph 'Wavelengths' DLC Official Trailer

node.text:
The #LifeisStrange Remastered Collection includes ‘Life is Strange Remastered’ and ‘Life is Strange: Before the Storm Remastered’.

Both award-winning games have been remastered with updated visuals across characters & environments.

node.title: Life is Strange Remastered Collection - E3 2021 Official Trailer

node.text:
#LifeisStrange #TrueColors launches this week. Here's a message to all fans to help keep the #SecretsOfHaven until everyone has gotten their hands on the game.⁣
⁣
STREAMERS: Please note streaming the game before the official release time - 9am PDT / 5pm BST on September 9 - will incur a takedown or strike. If you have an early copy of the game, please enjoy it privately and keep the #SecretsofHaven to yourself until then!
